aeus-un-controsenso.html | language =it | accessdate =June 28, 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Tong-il Security Medel Ribbon.svg|60px]]\n| [[Order of National Security Merit]], Tong-il Medal (Korea)\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:NLD Order of Orange-Nassau - Knight Grand Cross BAR.png|60px]]\n| Knight Grand Cross with Swords of the [[Order of Orange-Nassau]] (Netherlands)\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:POL Order Zaslugi RP kl3 BAR.png|60px]]\n| Commander's Cross of the [[Order of Merit of the Republic of Poland]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:POL Z\u0142oty Medal Wojska Polskiego BAR.svg|60px|Polish Army Medal (Gold)]]\n| [[Polish Army Medal]], Gold\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:POL Gwiazda Iraku BAR.svg|60px|Polish Iraq Star]]\n| [[Polish campaign stars|Polish Iraq Star]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Romanian Honor Emblem.png|60px|Romanian Emblem of Honor]]\n| Romanian Chief of Defense Honor Emblem<ref name=\"Questionnaire\">{{cite web | last =Select Committee on Intelligence | title =Questionnaire for Completion by Presidential Appointees | publisher =United States Senate | date =June 14, 2011 | url =http://intelligence.senate.gov/110623/questionnaire.pdf | accessdate =June 28, 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Grand Cross Military Merit Order UAE.png|60px]]\n| Military Merit Order, First Class (United Arab Emirates)\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:GEO Vakhtang Gorgasal Order 1rank BAR.svg|60px]]\n| Vakhtang Gorgasali Order, 1st Rank (Government of Georgia)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dfwatch.net/saakashvili-gives-hillary-clinton-the-golden-fleece-award-62137|title=Saakashvili gives Hillary Clinton the Golden Fleece award|work=Democracy & Freedom Watch}}</ref>\n|}\n|valign=\"top\" |\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#ccf; text-align:center;\"\n| colspan=2 |'''U.S. badges, patches and tabs'''\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Expert Infantry Badge.svg|110px]]\n|[[Expert Infantryman Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Combat Action Badge.svg|80p