avid Petraeus On The Complexities Of Re-Taking And Stabilizing Mosul |publisher=NPR |url=https://www.npr.org/2016/10/19/498504355/david-petraeus-on-the-complexities-of-re-taking-and-stabilizing-mosul?ft=nprml&f=2,3,46}}\n*{{Cite news|last=Petraeus|first=David |publication-date=October 20, 2016| year=2016|title=Petraeus says there's a bigger challenge to come once Iraq retakes Mosul from ISIS |publisher=PBS|url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/bb/petraeus-says-theres-bigger-challenge-come-iraq-retakes-mosul-isis/}}\n*{{Cite news|last=Petraeus|first=David H.|publication-date=February 1, 2017| year=2017|title=The State of the World |publisher=House Armed Services Committee|url=http://docs.house.gov/meetings/AS/AS00/20170201/105509/HHRG-115-AS00-Wstate-PetraeusD-20170201.pdf}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus |first=David H. |publication-date=March 29, 2017 |year=2017 |title=As Machines Wage War, Human Nature Endures|publisher=[[Berggruen Institute]] |url=http://berggruen.org/ideas/as-machines-wage-war-human-nature-endures}}\n* {{Cite web|last=Petraeus |first=David H. |publication-date=June 29, 2017 |year=2017 |title=Around the World in 60 Minutes|publisher=Aspen Ideas |url=https://www.aspenideas.org/session/around-world-60-minutes}}\n* {{Cite news|last=Babich |first=Jennifer. |publication-date=October 2, 2018 |year=2018 |title=Gen. David Petraeus recalls being shot while commanding at Fort Campbell|publisher=Leaf Chronicle|url=https://www.theleafchronicle.com/story/news/local/fort-campbell/2018/10/02/general-david-petreaus-fort-campbell-101st-airborne-division/1434072002/}}\n* {{Cite news|last=Reiss |first=Robert. |publication-date=October 2018 |year=2018 |title=The Leadership Issue|publisher=The CEO Forum|url=https://theceoforumgroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/leadership_whole_sm-compressed.pdf}}\n* {{cite news |last1=Petraeus |first1=David |last2=Whitehouse |first2=Sheldon |title=Putin and other authoritarians\u2019 corruption is a weapon \u2014 and a weakness |url=http