2984.htm?section=justin Order of Australia for General Petraeus], November 4, 2009, abc.net.au</ref><ref>[https://www.gg.gov.au/sites/default/files/files/honours/2009S172_Oct%2009.pdf Honorary Officer (AO) in the Military Division] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402034112/https://www.gg.gov.au/sites/default/files/files/honours/2009S172_Oct%2009.pdf |date=April 2, 2016 }}, November 3, 2009, Commonwealth of Australia Gazette, Special Issue No. S172</ref>\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:MSC ribbon-military.png|60px|Meritorious Service Cross (Canada)]]\n| [[Meritorious Service Cross]], Military Division (Canada)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.canada.ca/en/news.html|title=News|first=Service|last=Canada|date=August 31, 2016|website=aem}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:CZE Cross of Merit Min-of-Def 1st BAR.svg|60px]]\n| [[Cross of Merit of the Minister of Defence of the Czech Republic]], 1st Class\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Legion Honneur Commandeur ribbon.svg|60px]]\n| Commander of the [[Legion of Honour]] (France)\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Ruban de la M\u00e9daille comm\u00e9morative fran\u00e7aise.PNG|60px|Ribbon of the French commemorative Medal]]\n| [[M\u00e9daille comm\u00e9morative fran\u00e7aise|French Military Campaign Medal]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:GER Bundesverdienstkreuz 5 GrVK Stern.svg|60px]]\n| Knight Commander's Cross of the [[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Gold Award of the Iraqi Order of the Date Palm Ribbon.png|60px]]\n| Gold Award of the Iraqi Order of the Date Palm\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Croce al merito dei carabinieri gold medal BAR.svg|60px]]\n| Gold Cross of Merit of the Carabinieri (Italy)<ref>{{cite web | last =Comellini | first =Luca Marco | title =Croce d'Oro al Merito dell'Arma dei carabinieri al generale David Howell Petraeus, un controsenso | publisher =Tiscali SpA | url =http://notizie.tiscali.it/opinioni/Comellini/1232/articoli/Croce-d-Oro-al-Merito-dell-