iew/csgm |title=FSR Exclusive with David Petraeus |publisher=Fletcher Security Review |date=May 22, 2014 |accessdate=May 23, 2014}}</ref>\n* {{Cite news|last=Petraeus|first=David H.|publication-date=July 3, 2014|year=2014|title=POINT OF VIEW: Success of TPP negotiations is a national security necessity|newspaper=The Asahi Shimbun|url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/views/opinion/AJ201407030001|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726211758/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/views/opinion/AJ201407030001|archivedate=July 26, 2014|df=mdy-all}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H.|last2=Brown|first2=Neil R.|publication-date=July 11, 2014 |year=2014 |title=Mexico's miracle: Political productivity|newspaper=Houston Chronicle| url=http://www.chron.com/opinion/outlook/article/Mexico-s-miracle-Political-productivity-5616255.php}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |last2=O'Hanlon |first2=Michael |publication-date=September 5, 2014| year=2014 |title=Petraeus and O'Hanlon: Export-Import Bank an easy call|newspaper=USA Today|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/opinion/2014/09/05/export-import-petraeus-charter-renew-congress-column/14359985/}}\n* \"Report Launch of the CFR-Sponsored Independent Task Force on North America\", October 2, 2014<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GFqhR40x1_o |title=Report Launch of the CFR-Sponsored Independent Task Force on North America |date=October 2, 2014 |accessdate=October 3, 2014}}</ref>\n* \"Petraeus and Zoellick urge U.S. to pay attention to North America\", October 22, 2014<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fusion.net/video/23099/petraeus-and-zoellick-urge-u-s-to-pay-attention-to-north-america |title=Petraeus and Zoellick urge U.S. to pay attention to North America |date=October 21, 2014 |accessdate=October 22, 2014}}</ref>\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |last2=O'Hanlon |first2=Michael |publication-date=January 30, 2015| year=2015 |title=America on the way up|newspaper=The Washington Pos