hayani |first2=Paras |publication-date=June 25, 2015| year=2015 |title=An agenda of prosperity for America|publisher=CNN|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/25/opinions/petraeus-bhayani-innovation-america/}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |last2=Bhayani |first2=Paras D.|publication-date=June 25, 2015| year=2015 |title=North America: the Next Great Emerging Market?|work=Foreign Policy|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2015/06/25/north-america-the-next-great-emerging-market-united-states-mexico-canada//}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |last2=Bhayani |first2=Paras D.|publication-date=June 25, 2015| year=2015 |title=The Next Great Emerging Market?|publisher=Belfer Center|url=http://belfercenter.ksg.harvard.edu/publication/25488/next_great_emerging_market.html}}\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |last2=O'Hanlon |first2=Michael |publication-date=July 7, 2015| year=2015 |title=The U.S. needs to keep troops in Afghanistan|newspaper=The Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/afghanistan-after-obama/2015/07/07/63dd6dc2-1e8e-11e5-aeb9-a411a84c9d55_story.html}}\n* [http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/01/politics/david-petraeus-al-qaeda-isis-nusra/ \"EXCLUSIVE: Petraeus explains how jihadists could be peeled away to fight ISIS -- and Assad\"] Jake Tapper of ''CNN''; September 1, 2015\n* \"A Grand Strategy for \u2018Greater\u2019 Asia\", the Lowy Lecture (September 2015)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lowyinstitute.org/publications/lowy-lecture-2015-general-ret-david-petraeus-ao |title=Lowy Lecture 2015: General (Ret.) David Petraeus AO |publisher=Lowy Institute| date=September 2, 2015 |accessdate=September 2, 2015}}</ref>\n* {{Cite news |last=Petraeus|first=David H. |publication-date=March 26, 2016| year=2016|title=Brexit would weaken the West's war on terror|newspaper=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/eureferendum/12205094/David-Petraeus-Brexit-would-weaken-the-Wests-war-on-terror.html}}\n*{{Cite news |last=P